            <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD discussed the elaborate displays of male birds for females with respect to the sense of beauty in <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref> 1: 63–5 and 2: 71–9, 86–98.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">CD discussed the ornamentation of the argus pheasant in <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref> 2: 91–3 and 123–4.</note>
